sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User
    participant G as API Gateway
    participant S as Search Service
    participant C as Circuit Breaker
    participant E as Elasticsearch

    U->>G: GET /api/v1/search/ads?q=iphone
    G->>S: search request
    S->>C: call ES through breaker
    C->>E: query
    E--xC: timeout
    C-->>S: open/half-open state, fail fast
    S-->>G: 503 Service Unavailable
    G-->>U: error payload + retry advice
